Indication has emerged that Kogi State Governor Yahaya Bello will officially declare his presidential ambition on Saturday, April 2, at Eagle Square, Abuja. A member of the organising committee disclosed this to Daily Trust in Lokoja on Thursday, saying the governor will formally launch his presidential bid come Saturday. Bello had received several endorsements from across the geopolitical zones of the country, especially from youths and women whom, he said, are urging him to run for the exalted office.